Wednesday, May 13, 1992

MERIT DOCKET

92-427. State v. Ross.

Hamilton County, No. C-910769. On motion to dismiss or for extension of time. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright and Resnick, JJ., concur. H. Brown, J., dissents and would grant the motion for extension of time.
